      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped pepper</strong> and <strong>courgette</strong> to a <strong>baking paper</strong>-lined baking tray with the<strong> onion wedges</strong>, a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and put the tray in the oven for 20-25 min or until the vegetables are softened and golden – this is your <strong>roasted veg</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1679659430749-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1679659430749-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
