          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1679659435094-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, strip your <strong>mint leaves</strong> from their stems and chop them finely, discard the stems</p><p>Tip: Hold the top of the herb sprigs firmly and slide your fingers down their lengths to easily remove the leaves</p><p>Combine the<strong> chopped mint</strong> and<strong> natural yoghurt</strong> in a small bowl with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>mint yoghurt</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1679659441318-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
