            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1679659449242-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the rice is cooked, add your<strong> vegetable stock mix</strong> to the cooked rice and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>seasoned rice</strong></p><p>Once the roasted veg are softened and golden, remove the tray from the oven and transfer them to the seasoned rice and gently stir it all together – this is your <strong>roasted veg rice</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
