        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>roasted veg rice</strong> with the <strong>sticky chilli paneer</strong> on top</p><p>Drizzle over the<strong> mint yoghurt</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
